      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field validation against FDA experimental benchmark",
      "description": "CFD-predicted velocity fields compared against FDA benchmark PIV measurements across 5 operating conditions. GCI-based discretization error quantified. Normalized RMS error 8.3% across all planes. Validation performed under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which was the release candidate immediately preceding the current production build. The configuration was treated as effectively equivalent to the released build since only a minor patch resolving a non-hemolysis-related boundary condition logger was applied between rc2 and the final release; no re-execution of validation runs was performed under the released build.",
      "wasGeneratedBy": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/modelconfig/ansys-cfx-15-rc2",
