        "description": "Release candidate build immediately preceding ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7. Patch delta comprised only a fix to the post-processing boundary condition logger; solver numerics were asserted unchanged by the vendor. Validation team accepted this configuration as equivalent to the released build without re-running simulations."
