      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented SQA plan with version control, issue tracking, and regression testing suite covering hemolysis solver modules.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS CFX 15 is a commercial solver with documented SQA processes; however, the transition from rc2 to the released build was not accompanied by a solver-level regression test report specific to hemolysis predictions. SQA documentation references the rc2 build rather than the released version, leaving a gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
