      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup, boundary condition specification, and post-processing scripts by a qualified reviewer not involved in the original analysis.",
      "rationale": "No independent use-error review conducted. Simulation setup reviewed internally by the same analyst team. At MRL 5 for a Class III device, independent review is required; this factor is flagged as an epistemic gap."
    },
