      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain model inputs characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo UQ propagates input uncertainty to hemolysis index predictions.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed over 3 inputs (inlet velocity ±2%, dynamic viscosity ±5%, hemolysis power-law exponent ±10%). Wall roughness, rotational speed uncertainty, and blood rheology temperature dependence not included in UQ. Input characterization is incomplete relative to MRL 5 requirements."
